## 1. Scaffold Commands

```bash
# Run from upwork-runs/audio-software-engineer-needed-for/
npm create vite@latest demo-src -- --template react
cd demo-src
npm install
```

No extra audio npm packages. Web Audio API is browser-native. Only deps: `react`, `react-dom`, `vite`, `@vitejs/plugin-react`.

**vite.config.js** (exact):
```js
import { defineConfig } from 'vite'
import react from '@vitejs/plugin-react'
export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [react()],
  base: '/demos/audio-software-engineer-needed-for/',
})
```

**Build + deploy path:**
```bash
npm run build
# Then copy dist/* to:
# ../../../michaelwegter.com/public/demos/audio-software-engineer-needed-for/
```

